    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Skyward Steps Together》是一款第三人称多人平台跳跃游戏，背景设定在一个由神秘的“和谐之石”维持平衡的城市中。某个宁静的日子里，一股无法解释的宇宙能量突袭天空——这是一种几代人未曾见过的罕见自然现象。在这股能量的冲击下，和谐之石失去了稳定，最终破碎成碎片，散落在天空中。随着和谐之石的破裂，城市的平衡也随之崩溃，和平不再，不确定性悄然降临。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为城市中敏捷的跑酷者之一，你是恢复秩序的唯一希望。你的任务是收集散落的和谐之石碎片，将其重新拼合，并将城市恢复到往日的平衡状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多可支持四名玩家一同踏上冒险旅程，穿越充满挑战的跑酷路线，为城市带来和平与安宁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以单人冒险，也可以与好友组队游玩。最多支持四名玩家同时参与。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态技能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >架起空中平台，连接遥远的地点，跨越巨大的空隙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123610/extras/c628ba5e32d5eff071b0c425508a517c.poster.avif?t=1765725462\" width=456 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123610/extras/c628ba5e32d5eff071b0c425508a517c.webm?t=1765725462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123610/extras/c628ba5e32d5eff071b0c425508a517c.mp4?t=1765725462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瞬间传送至远处，轻松绕过困难地形。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123610/extras/4505f17a82804b8645bf17cecca09fc2.poster.avif?t=1765725462\" width=456 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123610/extras/4505f17a82804b8645bf17cecca09fc2.webm?t=1765725462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123610/extras/4505f17a82804b8645bf17cecca09fc2.mp4?t=1765725462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松越过障碍，攀登高处，拓展行动范围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123610/extras/234dff4fc410a3f07301d7475c305d5d.poster.avif?t=1765725462\" width=456 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123610/extras/234dff4fc410a3f07301d7475c305d5d.webm?t=1765725462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123610/extras/234dff4fc410a3f07301d7475c305d5d.mp4?t=1765725462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >滑翔机制</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用滑翔翼从高处安全降落。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巧妙选择落点，规划最佳路线。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集地图中散落的小型石片，为滑翔翼充能。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123610/extras/04e541fd76d354db83c9348d1f7bbaca.poster.avif?t=1765725462\" width=456 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123610/extras/04e541fd76d354db83c9348d1f7bbaca.webm?t=1765725462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123610/extras/04e541fd76d354db83c9348d1f7bbaca.mp4?t=1765725462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >史诗任务</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找大型石块碎片，作为关卡检查点。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战多样化的跑酷难关。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重铸古老的和谐之石，让城市重归平衡。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >排行榜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人或组队，在最短时间内恢复城市秩序，登上全球排行榜巅峰！</p>",
